    <h1 class="p-4 my-5 custom-title" style="font-size: 80px; font-weight: 700;">Permissions and Authorization</h1>
    <h5 class="mb-1 mt-5">Each models has those permissions.</h5>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-start mt-0">
        <h5 class="rounded mt-2 mb-2 p-3 custom-back">has_view_ModelName()</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-start mt-0">
        <h5 class="rounded mt-2 mb-2 p-3 custom-back">has_add_ModelName()</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-start mt-0">
        <h5 class="rounded mt-2 mb-2 p-3 custom-back">has_change_ModelName()</h5>
